CALL FOR PAPERS Workshop on Modeling and Simulation in Wireless Communication Systems July 19 , 1998 Montreal , Quebec , Canada
in conjunction with the Sixth International Symposium on Modeling , Analysis and Simulation of Computer and Telecommunication Systems ( [ 1 ] MASCOTS '98 ) July 19 - 24 , 1998 Complex Dejardins Hotel , Montreal , Canada
Wireless communication systems grow very fast these years . These systems become very large and complicated . That makes the analysis and evaluation of capacity and performance of wireless systems very difficult , if it is not impossible . Simulation is a frequently used approach to evaluate wireless systems . The Workshop on Modeling and Simulation in Wireless Communication Systems is a unique forum for presentation of recent advances in modeling and simulation of wireless communications systems .
Prospective authors are cordially invited to submit original , in-depth technical papers for presentation and publication in the workshop proceedings .
Topics of particular interest :
* FDMA , TDMA , CDMA system RF capacity simulation . * Simulation methodology of large scale wireless systems . * Performance evaluation of handoff , power control , registration and paging processes . * New simulation languages , tools for wireless systems . * Simulation and modeling topics in wireless networks and switches . * Simulation and modeling of wireless data and multimedia service * Simulation application of wireless protocols and standards .
The workshop will consist of paper presentations with in-depth discussion . It should be of interest to researchers and developers from academia and industry who are involved in the research , planning and developing wireless networks .
Deadlines :
Submission of manuscripts : March 20 , 1998 Notification of acceptance : May 20 , 1998 Final copy for proceedings : June 10 , 1998
Manuscripts should be in English and should be accompanied by a cover letter with name , affiliation , complete return address , telephone , FAX numbers and e-mail of the corresponding author . Send 4 copies of your manuscript to :
Hua Jiang Nortel M / S 99202 E 70 P . O . Box 833858 Richardson , TX 75083 - 3858 U . S . A .
